{"tid":2181654,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿蘇都檢測 美斯最終no show","createTime":"2020-08-30T17:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T01:38:36.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e75c8156a2bc1085a3d520700aa6f102571857a3","tid":2181654,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T17:37:24.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】一如外界預期，美斯最終沒有參與巴塞隆拿周日的新型冠狀病毒檢測，看來離隊之心堅決。其好友蘇亞雷斯則現身。<br />\n<br />\n巴塞隆拿於當地時間周日早上10時15分起為球員安排檢測，一眾戰將，包括會被賣走的蘇亞雷斯都獨個兒駕車現身，但新聞人物美斯（Lionel Messi）果然沒有現身訓練場。艾巴及有傳覬覦美斯10號球衣的比夫韋治率先到達接受檢測，而大軍將於周一在新帥朗奴高文監督下展開操練。<br />\n<br />\n根據防疫條例，球員若不進行測試，便不能夠在周一開操。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙著名體育記者Alfredo Martinez早於前一天在Twitter爆料，指美斯已經知會巴塞隆拿，周日不會回到Ciutat Esportiva訓練場，接受新型冠狀病毒測試。至於美斯或會因為這舉動而要繳付罰款，印證了他與球會的關係陷入低谷。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"8947bb15babbf9ee6d6dcc56ec64e0e56ae2dbed","tid":2181654,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T17:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EgqZFOXWAAQdXFl?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEgqZFOXWAAQdXFl%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D4096x4096&h=c7b146d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504c4036cfc67f343162a7695862f88e09e4951a","tid":2181654,"uid":40398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8947bb15babbf9ee6d6dcc56ec64e0e56ae2dbed","tid":2181654,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T17:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EgqZFOXWAAQdXFl?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEgqZFOXWAAQdXFl%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D4096x4096&h=c7b146d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class